gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 116, Trail Blazers 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Blazers, 116-107. Jalen Green (26 points, five 3PM, nine rebounds) led the Rockets as Amen Thompson added 17 points and 15 rebounds. Scoot Henderson led Portland with 30 points, a career-high six 3PM, and seven assists as Dalano Banton totaled 28 points and 10 rebounds.
